subject: Colleges and Universities
organizations: State University of New York at Binghamton
lead_paragraph: A woman who raises money for Binghamton University athletics has filed a complaint with the Equal Employment Opportunity Commission, alleging “egregious acts of sexual misconduct” by two senior athletic department officials.
